      "label": "EVER'lı Yapılar",
      "type": "examples",
      "items": [
        {
          "color": "pink",
          "tag": "WHATEVER — Ne / Her ne",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Tek başına (ergen/baştan savma)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever!</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>-I'll put my coat on the sofa.<br>-<font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever!</font> (Herneyse!)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Fiil + whatever</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font> + <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whatever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#00FFFF\">Eat</font> <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whatever</font> / <font color=\"#00FFFF\">Wear</font> <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whatever</font> makes you happy.</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whatever + fiil (fiili ikiletir)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever happens</font>, you must stay calm.<br>(Ne olursa olsun sakin kal.)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whatever + özne + fiil</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever you say</font> (ne söylersen söyle)<br>I won't believe in you, <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whatever you say!</font></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>Whatever + isim + özne + fiil</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">N</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>I trust you, <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whatever</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">decision</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">you</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">make</font>.</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "amber",
          "tag": "WHENEVER — Ne zaman / Her ne zaman",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Tek başına (uygun bir zamanda)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever.</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>-When should I bring your books?<br>-<font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever.</font></td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whenever + özne + fiil (ne zaman + fiili ikile)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>You can come <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whenever you want</font>.<br><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever it rains</font> in İstanbul, the streets flood.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>Her yapışımda havası (whenever = each time)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">I</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whenever I see her</font>, I smile.<br>(Onu her gördüğümde gülümserim.)</td></tr></tbody></table><br><b>⚠️ WHEN vs WHENEVER:</b><br>• <b>When I opened</b> the book, I saw her note. → O an (tek sefer)<br>• <b>Whenever I open</b> the book, I see her note. → Her seferinde (tekrarlı)"
        },
        {
          "color": "purple",
          "tag": "WHOEVER — Kim / Her kim",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whoever + fiil (fiili ikiletir)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whoever</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>I'll be happy, <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whoever wins</font>.<br>Don't answer the phone, <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whoever calls!</font></td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whoever + özne + fiil (kimi isterlerse)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whoever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>You can choose <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whoever you want</font>.<br>The people can vote for <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whoever they want</font> in democracies.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>Whoever özne olarak (her kim)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whoever</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font>, ... sonuç</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whoever finishes</font> the race first, gets the prize.<br><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whoever is responsible</font> for these crimes must be sent to jail.</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "blue",
          "tag": "WHICHEVER — Hangisi / Her hangisi (bir IT'i temsil eder)",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Tek başına</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Pick whichever.</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Hangisini istersen yiyebilirsin.</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Whichever + özne + fiil (hangisini + fiili ikile)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whichever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>You can buy <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whichever you prefer</font>.<br>Choose <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whichever you want</font>.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>Whichever + isim + özne + fiil</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whichever</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">N</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>You can borrow <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whichever</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">book</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">you</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">like</font> from the library.<br>Let's go to <font color=\"#FFFF00\">whichever</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">film</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">you</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">choose</font>.</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "green",
          "tag": "WHEREVER — Nerede / Nereye (bir yeri temsil eder)",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Tek başına (nereye istersen)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Wherever.</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>-Where should I leave this box?<br>-<font color=\"#FFFF00\">Wherever.</font></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>Wherever + özne + fiil (nerede + fiili ikile)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Wherever</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>I will find you <font color=\"#FFFF00\">wherever you live</font>.<br>She can go <font color=\"#FFFF00\">wherever she wants</font>.<br>Ayşe makes new friends <font color=\"#FFFF00\">wherever she goes</font>.</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "red",
          "tag": "HOWEVER — Nasıl / Ne kadar (2 farklı kullanım!)",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:35%;'>KULLANIM</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>Ancak / Ama anlamında (bağlaç)</td><td style='padding:8px;'>... <font color=\"#FFFF00\">however</font> ...</td><td style='padding:8px;'>It is rainy. <font color=\"#FFFF00\">However</font>, we want to be outside.<br>I wanted to go, <font color=\"#FFFF00\">however</font> I was busy.</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'>However it happens (nasıl olursa olsun)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">However</font> + it + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">However it happens</font>, I will solve it.<br>I'll be with you <font color=\"#FFFF00\">however it works out</font>.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'>However + sıfat + özne + fiil (ne kadar + fiili ikile)</td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">However</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">ADJ</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">S</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">However hard</font> I try → Ne kadar çok denersem deneyeyim<br><font color=\"#FFFF00\">However long</font> I searched → Ne kadar uzun süre ararsam arayayım</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "teal",
          "tag": "EVER'lı Yapılara Genel Bakış — Fiili İkiletme Tablosu",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px; table-layout: fixed;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:20%;'>EVER'LI</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:20%;'>TEMSİL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px; width:30%;'>ÖRNEK</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>TÜRKÇE</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FFFF00\">Whatever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Ne → What</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Whatever you do</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Sen ne yaparsan yap</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#00FF00\">Whenever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Ne zaman → When</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Whenever I see her</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Onu her gördüğümde</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#BA55D3\">Whoever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Kim → Who</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Whoever you call</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Sen kimi ararsan ara</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#00FFFF\">Whichever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Hangisi → Which</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Whichever you choose</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Hangisini seçersen seç</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF8C00\">Wherever</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Nerede → Where</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Wherever you go</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Nereye gidersen git</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF6B6B\">However</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Nasıl → How</td><td style='padding:8px;'>However you try</td><td style='padding:8px;'>Nasıl denersen dene</td></tr></tbody></table><br><b>💡 NO MATTER alternatifi:</b><br>Whatever you do = <b>No matter what</b> you do<br>Wherever you go = <b>No matter where</b> you go<br>Whenever I go = <b>No matter when</b> I go<br>Whoever you see = <b>No matter who</b> you see<br>Whichever you choose = <b>No matter which</b> you choose<br>However you do it = <b>No matter how</b> you do it"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
